![SM The World Cvr (Italy).jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1743439113032-2KXZNMD6AV7YEYGQWEZD/SM+The+World+Cvr+%28Italy%29.jpg) ![SMTWORLD_1_ITALY_Preview(1).jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1743439108952-KPWHY13LG17BJ2MH0B21/SMTWORLD_1_ITALY_Preview%281%29.jpg) ![SMTWORLD_1_ITALY_Preview(2).jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1743439119500-VLG6BGJF9O0OV5BKH255/SMTWORLD_1_ITALY_Preview%282%29.jpg)

**“Superman’s Inferno,” by Fabio Celoni and Marco Nucci (Italy)**

Acclaimed Italian comics creators Nucci and Celoni celebrate the incredible narrative of the Last Son of Krypton in this short story. In 2021, Clark Kent and Lois Lane are in the home city of the Sommo Poeta (the Supreme Poet), Dante Alighieri, on the 700th anniversary of his death. Suddenly, the earth splits open, with Lois and some bystanders swallowed up in a chasm that seems to lead directly to Hell. Superman’s only hope against the armies of Lucifer is tied to a formula seen in Dante’s visions that has been lost forever!

![SMTWRLD_1_JAPAN_Preview(1).jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1743439527189-7AKV51UDNF0BWWGICX7W/SMTWRLD_1_JAPAN_Preview%281%29.jpg)

![SMTWRLD_1_JAPAN_Preview(2).jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1743439525074-ISOK85PJSGT93DVRSDSH/SMTWRLD_1_JAPAN_Preview%282%29.jpg)

![SMTWRLD_1_JAPAN_Preview(1).jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1743439527189-7AKV51UDNF0BWWGICX7W/SMTWRLD_1_JAPAN_Preview%281%29.jpg) ![SMTWRLD_1_JAPAN_Preview(2).jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1743439525074-ISOK85PJSGT93DVRSDSH/SMTWRLD_1_JAPAN_Preview%282%29.jpg)

 **“Superman vs. Convenience-Store Dining Space,” by Satoshi Miyagawa and Kai Kitago (Japan)**

DC and Kodansha will include an excerpt from the popular DC manga _Superman vs. Meshi_, by Miyagawa and Kitago, readable in Western style (left to right).

![SMTWORLD_1_MEXICO_Preview(1).jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1743439466798-K4MZ0BMVHID3H3LWCTT8/SMTWORLD_1_MEXICO_Preview%281%29.jpg)

